senses.sense_text:
A man living at the time of Divided Monarchy, only mentioned at Hos.1.9; 
only referred to as Lo-ammi (לֹא עַמִּי); 
son of Hosea and Gomer; 
a brother of Jezreel, Lo-ruhamah. § symbolic name given by the prophet Hosea to his second son by Gomer

A woman living at the time of Divided Monarchy, first mentioned at Hos.1.6; 
only referred to as Lo-ruhamah (לֹא רֻחָ֫מָה); 
daughter of Hosea and Gomer; 
a sister of Jezreel, Lo-ammi H3818). § (Pual) symbolic name given by the prophet Hosea to his daughter
